name: Shalltear Bloodfallen LORA
description:
Lora of Shalltear Bloodfallen.

Use shalltear bloodfallen in prompt to call the lora, set lora strength to around 0.7~1.0 depending on model. model images were generated from abyssorangemix, deliberate, and pastelanimemix.

Use shalltearcostume as a prompt/neg prompt depending on what outfit you want, also adding "alternate costume" in prompt will help move it away from her original costume.
